particular, it hits people.

00:03:36.290 --> 00:03:37.480
It was very honest.

00:03:37.480 --> 00:03:40.354
It takes you places that
are really hard to go.

00:03:40.354 --> 00:03:42.020
One of the things I
wanted to get across

00:03:42.020 --> 00:03:44.830
